## Quick Ref

```
Stack manipulation:
  \f2Enter\fd=dup  \f2Tab\fd=swap
  \f2Backspace\fd=drop  \f2Del\fd=dropfirst
  \f2PageUp\fd=roll \f2PageDown\fd=unroll\fi

Math operators:
  \f2+ - * /
  \f2~\fd=neg
  \f2\\fd=idiv \f2%\fd=mod
  \f2^\fd=pow \f2@\fd=sq \f2$\fd=sqrt\fi
```

## Introduction

This calculator uses postfix notation (aka RPN): operators
must follow their operands. For example, to add 2 and 3
together, type "2(enter)3+".

Note: although it has an on-screen keyboard, the app is best
used with you physical keyboard.
